  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db7\u0dd6\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0db1\u0d9f\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A group of elite boarded two ships",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A video is circulating on social media showing a group of elites leaving the port of Colombo from the two ships Sidhurala and Gajaba belonging to the Sri Lanka Navy.",
        "It has not been confirmed who the dignitaries are, and it also shows a group of people hurriedly carrying their belongings and boarding the ship.",
        "Meanwhile, a convoy is also circulating on the social media as it travels along the Katunayake-Colombo Expressway."
      ],
